{"tid":1171292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"K11尋失物（卡套）","createTime":"2019-05-25T15:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T10:42:04.000Z","uid":3387,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e29a5aa13b8aa3f00bd59575fc5e4a587270b274","tid":1171292,"uid":3387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩大概夜晚10點左右係K11 2樓出邊坐低等食飯，<br />\n應該係果陣時跌左，唔知有冇巴絲咁岩係果頭汁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 雖然我知機會好渺茫，但都希望搵得....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡套： 啡色皮質（Brown公仔），內有身分證、學生證、八達通、銀行卡、信用卡及少量現金。<br />\n<br />\n已經報失，但入面有埋張身分證，過幾日就去旅行....煩請各位幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9efbca0ee1c606d83cf51a6365f2a8d772059f","tid":1171292,"uid":37116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"有無打俾K11 management office 問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd3bcb6f1d63376b42b9c1fec83ac19fdb7a714","tid":1171292,"uid":3387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9efbca0ee1c606d83cf51a6365f2a8d772059f","tid":1171292,"uid":37116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"有無打俾K11 management office 問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"打左啦，佢話冇，我留左電話同埋卡套資料比佢，等佢有消息可以打翻比我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse